en.name: ORSIS AR-15J .366 TKM assault carbine
en.description: The ORSIS-AR15J is a Russian civilian carbine developed in the late 2010s from the AR-15 platform chambered in .366 TKM and featuring a smoothbore barrel; this carbine is legally defined as a shotgun under Russian law.

en.name: AR-15J .366 TKM 20 inch barrel
en.description: A barrel for AR-15 based weapons for .366 TKM ammo, 20 inches long.

en.name: AR-15J .366 TKM 16 inch barrel
en.description: A barrel for AR-15 based weapons for .366 TKM ammo, 16 inches long.

en.name: AR-15J .366 TKM upper receiver
en.description: An upper receiver for the AR-15J assault carbine manufactured by ORSIS. Equipped with a mount for attaching additional devices.

en.name: Anderson AM-15 7.62x39 assault rifle
en.description: The Anderson AM-15 7.62x39 assault rifle is a 7.62x39mm assault rifle based on the AR-15 platform, offering the modularity of the AR platform with the stopping power of the 7.62x39mm round. Manufactured by Anderson Manufacturing.

en.name: AM-15 7.62x39 20 inch barrel
en.description: A barrel for AR-15 based weapons for 7.62x39 ammo, 20 inches long.

en.name: AM-15 7.62x39 16 inch barrel
en.description: A barrel for AR-15 based weapons for 7.62x39 ammo, 16 inches long.

en.name: AM-15 7.62x39 upper receiver
en.description: An upper receiver for the AM-15 assault rifle manufactured by Anderson Manufacturing. Equipped with a mount for attaching additional devices.
